text: Neketh Gedara Roshan Prabath Jayasuriya is a cricketer from Sri Lanka. Jayasuriya plays for the Sri Lanka national cricket team. He was born on November 5, 1991.Prabath Jayasuriya == References == == Other websites == Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Sri Lankan cricketers
